            <h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size:1.35rem;">Warmth & Movement</h3>
            <p>
              Thermal baths are inviting without freezing, river walks are lush, and the cultural calendar
              hums quietly—it's a balanced introduction to Budapest’s duality.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1; min-width:220px;">
            <div class="label">Seasonal Notes</div>
            <h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size:1.35rem;">Layered & Returnable</h3>
            <p>
              Winter’s steam-filled nights, summer’s riverbank festivals, and spring’s bloom all offer
              reasons to come back—each visit writes a slightly different chapter.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

